sql:
SELECT site_name
FROM dating_sites
WHERE is_active = 1 AND country = 'China';

SELECT site_id, SUM(total_members) AS total_members_per_site
FROM membership_data
GROUP BY site_id;

SELECT review_title
FROM editor_reviews
WHERE rating = 5;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS active_sites_count
FROM dating_sites
WHERE is_active = 1;

SELECT description
FROM site_features
WHERE is_supported = 1 AND feature_priority = 'high';

external_knowledge:
- Public membership data refers to information about members that is available to everyone; 
- Average user rating is an indicator of how well a site is liked by its users; 
- Average daily time spent is a metric that measures user engagement by calculating the average time users spend on the site each day;
- Reviewed sites are those that have been evaluated by editors.
